('50', 'BBA', '<div class=\"container-fluid event\">\r\n        <h1 class=\"text-center\" style=\"text-decoration: underline\"> BBA PROGRAMS</h1>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-top: 50px;\">\r\n            \r\n                <div class=\"col-sm-2\">\r\n                        \r\n                    </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n                       <a href=\"#\"> <div class=\"card\">\r\n                            <img class=\"card-img-top img-fluid\" src=\"../assets/bbaa.png\" alt=\"Card image cap\">\r\n                            <div class=\"card-block\">\r\n                                <p class=\"card-text card-body text-center\" style=\"font-size: 23px\"><b>BBA 4 year</b>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div></a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n              \r\n                    <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n                           <a href=\"#\" > <div class=\"card\">\r\n                                <img class=\"card-img-top img-fluid\" src=\"../assets/bbaa.png\" alt=\"Card image cap\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-block\">\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-text card-body text-center\" style=\"font-size: 23px;\"><b>BBA speacialzation courses</b>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div></a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n        \r\n                        <div class=\"col-sm-2\">\r\n                        \r\n                            </div>\r\n                   \r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n                   \r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n</div>', 1),
('6', 'Vice Chanceller Message', '<div class=\"chancellor container-fluid\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div >\r\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 \">\r\n      <h1 class=\"text-center heading\"> VICE CHANCELLOR’S MESSAGE</h1>\r\n      <div class=\"card\" style=\"width: 18rem; float: right\">\r\n        <img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"../assets/m1.jpg\" alt=\"Card image cap\" style=\"height: 330px;\">\r\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n          <p class=\"card-text text-center\">\r\n            <b>Prof. Dr. Vali Uddin</b>,<i>VICE Chancellor-SSUET</i>\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <a href=\"../Messages\"><button class=\"backbtn\"><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-left\"></i></button></a>\r\n      <div class=\" message\">\r\n      <p>\r\n            Sir Syed University of Engineering & Technology –SSUET is built on the philosophy of philanthropy of Sir Syed Ahmed Khan and a system of modern education as we move forward towards a knowledge based economy and meeting the challenges of the 4th industrial revolution.\r\n<br>\r\nIn the early 1990s, the campus of SSUET was established in the centre of Karachi city within the immediate vicinity of educational corridor. It can be reached conveniently from all corners of the City.<br>\r\nIn the early 1990s, the campus of SSUET was established in the centre of Karachi city within the immediate vicinity of educational corridor. It can be reached conveniently from all corners of the City.<br>\r\nThe vision of the University is to deliver first-class teaching supported by research that is rigorous and Prof. Dr. Muhammad Afzal Haque Vice Chancellor relevant to the social and economic priorities of the country and of the region, sustaining Academic Disciplines and Professions and propagating our Culture and Values.<br>\r\nWe also now aim to provide a platform for our students to incubate and create startup companies with the help of mentors and Venture Capital funds to be attracted with the help of national and international agencies.<br>\r\nOur technology based research has social impact with global effect. People here are endeavoring to increase entrepreneur’s yields to feed the nation, educating youth to be available for country and across the world. Research grants and scholarships are two of the ways in which we are supporting emerging researchers at SSUET for carrying out life-changing research.<br>\r\nWe are planning to offer research-led entrepreneurial education and typifying our covenant to excellence in research and education, we expect our faculty members to be great researchers while maintaining the attributes of good teachers. Thanks to our sponsors and supporters, we are able to make Sir Syed Ahmed Khan’s vision of education available to the widest possible ambit of students. For example since the inception of SSUET we have worked with various national and international allies to deliver scholarship to every promising student while the internship opportunities for students are also created at SSUET.<br>\r\nThe reputation of SSUET for student life is based on principles of learning in an environment of diversity and inclusion. We offer a prodigious range of extra-curricular activities, societies and forums, sports, art and an extravagant programme of volunteering. These opportunities are essential to produce the dynamic students that are able to take on the world. We place great emphasis on the grooming of students and inculcate in them the Aligarh spirit of ‘rising to the occasion’.\r\n<br>\r\nWe welcome you to join us in opening up the potential of the young, brilliant minds, in working together on ground-breaking research outcomes, and in creating an entrepreneurial world.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Prof. Dr. Vali Uddin</b>\r\n<br>\r\nVice Chancellor\r\n\r\n\r\n      </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1),
('7', 'Registratar Message', '<div class=\"chancellor container-fluid\">\r\n    \r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div >\r\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 \">\r\n      <h1 class=\"text-center heading\"> VICE CHANCELLOR’S MESSAGE</h1>\r\n      <div class=\"card\" style=\"width: 18rem; float: right\">\r\n        <img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"../assets/m3.jpg\" alt=\"Card image cap\" style=\"height: 330px;\">\r\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n          <p class=\"card-text text-center\">\r\n            <b>Engr. Syed Sarfraz Ali</b>,<i>Registrar - SSUET\r\n                </i>\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <a href=\"../Messages\"><button class=\"backbtn\"><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-left\"></i></button></a>\r\n      <div class=\" message\">\r\n            Sir Syed University of Engineering Technology has a unique character in that it is amongst the very few Universities of the world which has been established exclusively by the Alumni to repay their debt. The Alumni of Aligarh University (India), as their moral obligation and national duty, have exclusively contributed to the establishment of Sir Syed University of Engineering & Technology to reintroduce and rejuvenate the noble cause and mission of Sir Syed Ahmed Khan and to provide excellence in educating the youth of this country. Now that the foundation has been laid, it is the duty of all of us to keep this university abreast with the latest developments in the field of Engineering and Science.<br>\r\n            With a long term vision and clearly defined strategic milestones, the Management of SSUET has embarked upon this overwhelming task of bringing this University at par with leading International Institutions. Hence all efforts are underway for transforming Sir Syed University into a truly modern, state of the art and elite University of 21st Century. What is now required is a focused and full hearted support of each and every stakeholder of the University to achieve this monumental and historical task.\r\n            <br>\r\n            The Faculty, Alumni, Students and Staff once again need to work with the same ‘Aligarh Spirit’ to transform Sir Syed University of Engineering & Technology into one of the top National University and  let it be written down in the history that: ‘They were the ones who did it’.<br>\r\n            I welcome and assure all new students that by choosing to study in Sir Syed University of Engineering & Technology they have made the ‘Right Decision’. Together we shall excel in all fields of Engineering and Sciences.<br>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <b>Engr. Syed Sarfraz Ali</b>\r\n            Registrar - SSUET\r\n      </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n ', 1),
('8', 'Dean Message', '<div class=\"chancellor container-fluid\">\r\n    \r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div >\r\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 \">\r\n      <h1 class=\"text-center heading\"> DEAN (FOE)’S MESSAGE</h1>\r\n      <div class=\"card\" style=\"width: 18rem; float: right\">\r\n        <img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"../assets/m2.jpg\" alt=\"Card image cap\" style=\"height: 330px;\">\r\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n          <p class=\"card-text text-center\">\r\n            <b>Prof. Dr. Talat Altaf</b>,<i>Dean, faculty of Engineering\r\n                </i>\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <a href=\"../Messages\"><button class=\"backbtn\"><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-left\"></i></button></a>\r\n      <div class=\" message\">\r\n            On the occasion of launching of an up-to-date web site of SSUET.<br>\r\n            I am delighted to say that an up-to-date version of SSUET web site has been launched for providing detailed information about the University and its programs for the benefit of all stake-holders and public at large. Besides, the regular undergraduate, graduate & postgraduate programs and Continuous Education Programs, new initiatives like Campus on Cloud (CoC), ORIC, Guidance Centre and Quality Enhancement Cell have been added to get full picture about the organizational growth. SSUET is a forward looking organization and most of the information and data is unreservedly made public for common knowledge of people in order to take full advantage out of its free access.<br>\r\n            I hope the students, researchers, R&D set-ups, faculty, staff, parents and other organizations will find it a very useful link and will make use of it freely.<br>\r\n            It is said that the first impression is the last impression.  Therefore, website of any entity plays a significant role in creating the early impression about the organization when you visit its website even before physical contact or actual interaction with the organization and its people. Moreover, the information incorporated in the website should be in presentable, attractive and understandable form.<br>\r\n            While designing the new SSUET website all these aspects have been adequately taken care of.<br>\r\n            I congratulate the staff concerned for designing and launching the website for SSUET which was long overdue.<br>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <br>\r\n            Prof. Dr. Talat Altaf\r\n            <br>\r\n            Dean, faculty of Engineering\r\n      </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n ', 1),
('9', 'Mission and Vision', '<div class=\"chancellor container-fluid\">\r\n  <div class=\"row \">\r\n    <div >\r\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 \">\r\n      <h1 class=\"text-center intro\"> Mission</h1>\r\n     \r\n      \r\n      <div class=\" message\">\r\n            To play a leading role as a University of Engineering and Technology in national socio-economic development meeting the challenges of modern time by creating alliances and partnerships between academia and industry. To focus on innovation, research and commercialization, a sense of social and moral responsibility and imbued with the Aligarh spirit.\r\n\r\n\r\n      </div>\r\n      <br>\r\n      <br>\r\n       <h1 class=\"text-center intro\"> Vision </h1>\r\n      <div class=\"message\">\r\n            SSUET vision is to meet the demands of challenging times as envisioned by Sir Syed Ahmed Khan by transforming Pakistan into a Knowledge based society through social impact projects and innovation in education, research and creativity, endeavoring to create an entrepreneurial mindset.\r\n\r\n      </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1);

